title: NCIS Complete Season 12 mp4 720x404
description:
All 24 episodes of NCIS on MP4. 

All episodes are MP4s; They are 720x404 video resolution. Audio wise, they are H264, AAC, but I really have no idea what that means. You'll have to forgive me for not knowing all the tech specs, this is my first video upload.

All I did was go around, find all the episodes other folks had uploaded to various torrent sites, converted a few .mkv files to .mp4 format so they'd all be the same codec, and then bundled them together. I saw someone had done something similar for season 11, so figured I'd take the time to do it for Season 12. I'm just trying to be helpful and save the next person the time of doing so. If I should do something differently, or not bother in the future, please post in the comments. Thx
